This chart visualizes Power BI measures like completed orders, active users, and signups. It combines a line chart with points showing trends, along with a bottom table displaying values and week-over-week changes (Î”). Negative changes are highlighted in red, making dips easy to spot.

Special features:
- Interactive metric selector (based on Power BI measures)
- Conditional formatting for negative changes
- Shared x-axis with clean, aligned table for quick reference
